# Backlog — Future Improvements

Items discovered during L0 development that are out of scope but worth tracking.

## L1 Candidates

### Search & Filtering
- [ ] **Sanitize SQL wildcards in search** — Search terms with `%` or `_` are SQL wildcards in `ilike`. If user searches `%`, it matches everything. Add input sanitization.
  - Source: T023 implementation
  
- [ ] **Add GIN index for text search** — No index on `indicators.name`. For large datasets, add a GIN index with `pg_trgm` for faster text search.
  - Source: T023 implementation

